---
title: Carne Asada-Style Steak & Fries with Queso, Corn Chips & Salsa Verde
description: Some say that carne asada (literally translates to "grilled meat") is the best way to enjoy a steak and we'll be inclined to agree after tasting this fancy Mexican-style feast. Tender, juicy steak is topped with a herby salsa verde, best enjoyed with a side of queso and crunchy corn chips for dipping. The hardest part about this tasty collection of dishes is what to dig into first!
